Ken Wayne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ken_Wayne 0 Kenneth Dewayne "Ken" Peale (born January 15, 1959), better known by the ring name "Nightmare" Ken Wayne, is an American retired professional wrestler. He is the founder and owner of New Experience Wrestling, as well as a board member of Ohio Valley Wrestling.
